name: Centenary Church PI / Brazil (Editions: 1/1)
description: This oil painting is a reminder of the centenary Church that I saw when I traveled in the interior of Piauí / Brazil when I was a child and has been in my possession since 1981. Now I´m transforming all my oil paintings and artwork into NFT, in this way, this artwork will be unique and exclusive for the new collector. Contact: marcelovpessoa@gmail.com
